            care.
        </div>

        <p>
           A more comprehensive array of screening steps is evolving as more is learned about MS, therapies used and its interactions with body systems<sup>100-102</sup>. Vitamin D levels, herpes virus status, and thyroid function tests are moving to the forefront<sup>99</sup> (figure 7). 

        </p>

